Acterys Variance

 

Render KPI cards with result vs comparison and variance indicators as well as different chart display options (absolute, relative, waterfall) in a vertical or horizontal small multiple display.

Features:

  • Switch between absolute and relative variance display
  • Fully configurable KPI indicator display
  • Option to display total across all cards
  • Zoom into charts
  • Category drill down
  • Write back, planning and forecasting (requires Acterys subscription)
  • Supports all Power BI features like custom tool tips and drill through
